column2: <c=@abilitytype>Command.</c>Your pet teleports a downed ally within range of you and begins reviving them. Grant regeneration to nearby allies.
Gain access to a glider so that you can glide across the highest points of the Heart of Maguuma as well as Central Tyrian open-world maps.
Double-click to apply to an unused infusion slot. Infuses armor with a Super aura.
